    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>混沌公司：祝你好运，成为本周最佳员工！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你刚刚入职多元宇宙中最难以预测的店铺，你的工作是为络绎不绝追逐英雄梦想的人们制造并售卖标志性物品；与此同时，你的设备会突然拥有生命，同事们惊慌失措，人力资源部对你置之不理，而周五就像最终 BOSS 般压得人喘不过气来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在零售业的这个地狱中熬过一周吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制造标志性物品</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组装经典冒险装备——宝剑、藏宝图、魔法花、隐形斗篷等等，并出售给一群要求十分苛刻的“英雄”顾客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作台有自己的想法，所以你需要制定策略，同时处理多项任务，并随机应变！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/c7a924ad7378e57f7f6d187f2e331421.poster.avif?t=1771257739\" width=1170 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/c7a924ad7378e57f7f6d187f2e331421.webm?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/c7a924ad7378e57f7f6d187f2e331421.mp4?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>驯服你的设备</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每件设备都有自己的个性……以及不良习惯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让它们开心才能提升效率、解锁方便的自动化功能，还能防止某台设备在工作期间溜出去喝咖啡。面对挑剔的顾客和情绪不稳定的硬件，你很难分清自己究竟在为谁工作。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/058ee4a360eb326e5ad7f99b69bef1ab.poster.avif?t=1771257739\" width=1170 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/058ee4a360eb326e5ad7f99b69bef1ab.webm?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/058ee4a360eb326e5ad7f99b69bef1ab.mp4?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>维持店铺经营</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划每周的工作内容，在顾客之间周旋，应对混乱局面，做好迎接周五客流高峰的准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在为那些一心想当英雄的顾客服务的同时，别被那些桀骜不驯的设备（或同事）逼疯。每一天都是对你的考验，要在完成公司的业绩与彻底崩溃之间寻求平衡。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/a62f46e76163dab294a8dfcefba6c6ba.poster.avif?t=1771257739\" width=1170 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/a62f46e76163dab294a8dfcefba6c6ba.webm?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/a62f46e76163dab294a8dfcefba6c6ba.mp4?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelite 式的重玩性</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在混沌公司，每周都不一样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级设备、调整布局、优化工作流程，以应对不断升级的混乱！每次游戏都能发现新设备、店铺布局、可制作的物品和出乎意外的事件。完善你的日常流程，打破先前的利润纪录，或者干脆再次陷入疯狂。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/8d3b0f56c722c758015fb18cce3779c6.poster.avif?t=1771257739\" width=1170 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/8d3b0f56c722c758015fb18cce3779c6.webm?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/8d3b0f56c722c758015fb18cce3779c6.mp4?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>单人游戏或合作经营</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自经营店铺，或与最多 4 位好友进行在线或本地合作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协调轮班、分担任务，并就锤子为什么（再次）不见了而争论不休。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团队协作并非必须，但截止日期不容错过。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/44a62bba489d939ad559cea514e78505.poster.avif?t=1771257739\" width=1170 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/44a62bba489d939ad559cea514e78505.webm?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317020/extras/44a62bba489d939ad559cea514e78505.mp4?t=1771257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持 4 名玩家在线及本地合作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为各种冒险者制造标志性的装备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驯服调皮捣蛋的设备（或者忍受它们的坏脾气）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划、升级并优化你的店铺布局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每周面对新的挑战与事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelite 游戏机制，融合了幽默元素，极具反复重玩的价值与策略性</p></li></ul>",
